        "Description": [
          {
            "text": "Built for outdoor adventurers, our versatile magnesium alloy fire flint is the ultimate emergency survival tool for campers, hikers, hunters, and outdoor enthusiasts. This multi-functional kit includes a steel fire stick, built-in compass, emergency whistle, lanyard, tinder scraper, map scale, and bottle opener. With a long lifespan, it ensures reliable fire starting in almost any situation, from rain and snow to extreme altitudes. The compact, lightweight design fits easily in pockets, backpacks, or camping gear, and can be worn around the neck for quick access. Crafted from durable magnesium alloy, this weatherproof and waterproof fire starter is ideal for both emergency survival scenarios and regular camping trips. It’s a must-have addition to any outdoor safety equipment, offering convenience and reliability when you need it most. Suitable for hunting, wilderness exploration, fishing, and camping, this portable tool combines functionality with durability to meet all your outdoor fire-starting needs.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
