        "备注": "[\"登山类用品\"]",
        "完整描述": "Built for outdoor adventurers, our versatile magnesium alloy fire flint is the ultimate emergency survival kit for campers, hikers, hunters, and anyone who loves the outdoors. This multi-tool includes a steel fire stick, built-in compass, emergency whistle, lanyard, tinder scraper, map scale, and bottle opener. Our fire starter has a long lifespan, ensuring you can start a fire in almost any situation. This tool is weatherproof and waterproof, so it works well in rain, snow, and extreme altitude conditions. The compact size makes it easy to fit in a pocket, backpack, or camping gear, and can even be worn around the neck for quick access. Whether you are facing an emergency survival situation or just enjoying a camping trip, this multi-tool is the perfect choice for you.",
